{% doc %}
  Exposes translations as a JSON object that can be consumed by JavaScript.

  The keys correspond to entries in the theme (or extension) locale files,
  such as locales/en.default.json. Values are resolved using the `t` filter
  so they are automatically localized to the current storefront language.

  @example
  {% render 'digitalcoo-translations' %}
{% enddoc %}

